hana trigonometric: He hana o ka huina i hoikeia ma ke ano he ratio o ka loa o na aoao o ka huinakolu huina kupono
hana inverse: He hana i loaʻa ma ka hōʻike ʻana i ka loli hilinaʻi o kekahi hana ma ke ʻano he hoʻololi kūʻokoʻa o kekahi
arctangent: Ka hana inverse o ka tangent
arcsine: Ka hana inverse o ka sine
arccosine: Ka hana inverse o ka cosine
kosecant: ʻO ka pānaʻi o ka hana sine, i wehewehe ʻia ʻo ka ratio o ka hypotenuse i ka ʻaoʻao ʻaoʻao o kahi huinakolu ʻākau.
cotangent: ʻO ka pānaʻi o ka hana tangent, i wehewehe ʻia ʻo ia ka ratio o ka mea pili i ka ʻaoʻao ʻaoʻao o kahi huinakolu ʻākau.
\u02bbike pili trigonometric: He kaulike e pili ana i na hana trigonometric i pololei no na waiwai a pau o na hoololi
kanawai o na sine: I loko o ka huinakolu, ua mau ka ratio o ka loa o kekahi aoao me ka sine o kona huina kue
k\u0101n\u0101wai o n\u0101 cosines: I loko o ka huinakolu, ua like ka huinahalike o kekahi aoao me ka huina o na huinahalike o na aoao elua e hoemi ana i ka palua o ka huina hoonui o keia mau aoao elua a me ka cosine o ka huina hui.
ana radian: ʻO ke ana o ka huina i loko o nā radians, ʻo ia ka ratio o ka lōʻihi o kahi arc i kona radius
velocity angular: Ka nui o ka hoʻololi ʻana o kahi kihi e pili ana i ka manawa
l\u014d\u02bbihi arc: ʻO ka mamao ma waena o ʻelua mau kiko ma kahi ʻāpana o ka ʻalihi
\u02bb\u0101pana: ʻO ka ʻāpana o ka pōʻai i hoʻopaʻa ʻia e nā radii ʻelua a me ko lākou poʻe i hoʻopaʻa ʻia
ratio trigonometric: Ka ratio o ka loa o na aoao elua o ka huinakolu kupono
ho\u02bboh\u0101likelike trigonometric: He hoohalike e pili ana i hookahi a i ole ia mau hana trigonometric o ka hoololi
